  "novel_contributions": [
    "We introduce MobileViT, a light-weight and general-purpose vision transformer for mobile devices.",
    "We introduce the MobileViT block that encodes both local and global information in a tensor effectively.",
    "We extend multi-scale training to variably-sized batch sizes with a multi-scale sampler for training efficiency.",
    "We show that light-weight ViTs can achieve light-weight CNN-level performance with simple training recipes across different mobile vision tasks."
  ],
